data.description: Beautiful two story home in the heart of Blooming Grove.  This home features three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms.  The layout and design makes it perfect for entertaining with massive living room, open dining area, and spacious kitchen.  The kitchen has granite countertops, Jenn-Air gas range, and a large walk-in pantry.  The primary suite is located on the first floor and has a oversized walk-in closet, ensuite bathroom with double sinks and large shower.  On the second level you will find two large bedrooms with full hall bathroom.  Step out back to the covered porch and massive fenced in back yard.  This yard is the perfect place to play with wood privacy fence.  Don't miss your chance for small town living with only short drive to Corsicana or Waxahachie.  Call today to set you property tour.
